    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those suggestions. i've heard about lincoln park, so that sounds good. but i was also thinking about some of the areas closer to the downtown or more central parts of the city. i don't want to be too far out in the suburbs, but i also don't want to head into parts of the city that might be more \"unpredictable\" or have higher crime rates. are there certain types of areas or specific blocks i should steer clear of just to be safe?",
