      "content": "If you want to stay central but safe, areas like River North or the Gold Coast are good bets, though they can be more pricey. Generally, when in the downtown area, stick to the highly visible, well-lit commercial streets and avoid venturing down side streets, especially late at night. Certain blocks in the immediate vicinity of major transit hubs or areas with heavy nightlife can be unpredictable, so just rely on your instincts and stick to the main thoroughfares.",
